Mayorfirst,SMS,is,a,web,based,messaging,service,for,sending,invitations,notifications,advertisements,etc,Developers,can,access,the,Mayorfirst,SMS,messaging,gateway,using,a,RESTful,API,This,allows,users,to,integrate,the,ability,to,send,messages,and,check,their,account,balances,into,their,own,websites,and,applications,Mayorfirst,SMS,also,provides,a,RESTful,API,for,resellers